---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Our Letter to You | The Sellers Family" description="A personal letter from Daniel and Katie Sellers to expectant parents considering adoption.">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-warm-800 mb-8 text-center">
      Our Letter to You
    </h1>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-8 md:p-12 font-serif text-warm-800 leading-relaxed">
      <p class="text-lg mb-6">Dear Friend,</p>

      <!-- OPENING: Acknowledge their courage, express gratitude -->
      <p class="mb-4">
        Thank you for taking the time to read this. We know you are making
        one of the most important decisions of your life, and we want you to
        know that we see you, we respect you, and we honor whatever path you
        choose.
      </p>

      <!-- WHO WE ARE: Brief intro -->
      <p class="mb-4">
        <!-- TODO: 2-3 sentences about your family. Who you are, your vibe. -->
        [Brief family introduction — to be filled in]
      </p>

      <!-- WHY ADOPTION: Honest explanation -->
      <p class="mb-4">
        <!-- TODO: Why are you choosing adoption? Be honest and brief. -->
        [Your reason for choosing adoption — to be filled in]
      </p>

      <!-- WHAT LIFE LOOKS LIKE: Paint a picture -->
      <p class="mb-4">
        <!-- TODO: What would a day, a week, a holiday look like for this child in your home? Be specific and sensory. Saturday mornings, bedtime routines, holiday traditions. -->
        [A picture of daily life — to be filled in]
      </p>

      <!-- YOUR KIDS AS SIBLINGS -->
      <p class="mb-4">
        <!-- TODO: How do E and C feel about a new sibling? What kind of siblings would they be? -->
        E and C are so ready for this. [More about your kids' excitement — to be filled in]
      </p>

      <!-- OPEN ADOPTION COMMITMENT -->
      <p class="mb-4">
        We believe in open adoption — not as an obligation, but as a gift
        to your child and to you. We want you to be part of this child's
        story, always. That means photos, updates, calls, and visits — as
        much or as little as feels right for you.
        <!-- TODO: Adjust this to reflect your actual comfort level with openness -->
      </p>

      <!-- CLOSING -->
      <p class="mb-4">
        Whatever you decide, we want you to know: you are brave, you are
        loved, and your child is lucky to have a parent who cares this much
        about their future.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-8">
        With love and hope,<br />
        <span class="font-semibold">Daniel, Katie, E & C Sellers</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-8">
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-sage-600 text-white rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-sage-700 transition-colors">
        Get in Touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
